nodes.text: Duel between The Dreamer and The Monster-Slayer
According to Luke Skywalker, the legend was rooted in fact, and took place circa 3400 BBY.
At some point, a depiction of the duel came into Skywalker's possession, which he annotated sometime after the Emperor's death in 11 ABY along with a copy of The Jedi Path and Book of Sith.
